    "summary_short": "With the Queen of Hearts reformed and Cinderella safe, Red and Chloe believe life is perfect until their past changes spawn a new threat. Maddox Hatter, the son of the Mad Hatter, emerges as a villain and captures the Queen of Hearts. Red and Chloe must join forces with Red’s new sister Pink, Luis (son of Luisa Madrigal), and Max (Maddox’s son) to mount a rescue. Together, they fight to save both the Queen of Hearts and the fate of Wonderland.",
    "summary_long": "Following the events that turned the Queen of Hearts nice and ensured Cinderella’s safety, Red and Chloe enjoy what seems like a perfect life in a peacefully restored timeline. However, their interference with the past has unforeseen consequences that give rise to a brand-new antagonist: Maddox Hatter, the son of the original Mad Hatter. Maddox, embittered or driven by his own agenda, captures the now-kind Queen of Hearts and threatens the stability of Wonderland. Realizing the danger, Red and Chloe quickly regroup and seek help from unexpected sources. They are joined by Pink, Red’s newly introduced sister, who brings her own perspective and abilities to the mission. Luis, the son of Luisa Madrigal from the Madrigal family, adds strength and heart to the team. Max, the son of the villain Maddox Hatter himself, becomes a conflicted but crucial ally who understands his father’s plans. The group navigates the bizarre and magical landscapes of Wonderland to locate the captured queen. Along the way, they confront traps and challenges orchestrated by Maddox to test their unity. In the end, the young heroes must combine their courage and family bonds to rescue the Queen of Hearts and protect Wonderland from Maddox’s schemes.",
